testsuite.name: graphql.TypeResolverExecutionTest

testcase.name: happy case, type resolution should work
interface: when typeResolver returns an aberrant type it should yield a GraphQL error
interface: when typeResolver returns an aberrant type and the field is non-nullable, it should yield a GraphQL error
interface: when typeResolver returns null (meaning it couldn't find an appropriate type), it should yield a UnresolvedTypeError GraphQL error
interface: when typeResolver returns null and the field is non-nullable, it should yield an UnresolvedTypeError GraphQL error
union: when typeResolver returns an aberrant type it should yield a GraphQL error
union: when typeResolver returns an aberrant type and the field is non-nullable, it should yield a GraphQL error
union: when typeResolver returns null (meaning it couldn't find an appropriate type), it should yield a UnresolvedTypeError GraphQL error
union: when typeResolver returns null and the field is non-nullable, it should yield an UnresolvedTypeError GraphQL error
